Wednesday, April 22, 1998

MERIT DOCKET

97-859. Utility Workers Union of Am., AFL-CIO v. Pub. Util. Comm.

Public Utilities Commission, No. 96-406-EL-COI. On motion to dismiss. Motion to dismiss sustained. Cause dismissed.

Moyer, C.J., Bryant, Cook and Lundberg Stratton, JJ., concur. Douglas, F.E. Sweeney and Pfeifer, JJ., dissent. Peggy Bryant, J., of the Tenth Appellate District, sitting for Resnick, J.
